{{vgname2|Xbox娱乐工作室|en=Xbox Entertainment Studios}}，是总部设在美国加州圣莫尼卡的电视和电影工作室{{Inconsistent}}，在2012年由微软工作室在内部创建，以方便Xbox Live创建“互动电视内容。”<ref>{{cite web |last=Farber |first=Dan |url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-1023_3-57568826-93/microsofts-xbox-entertainment-studio-working-on-interactive-tv/ |title=Microsoft's Xbox Entertainment Studio working on interactive TV |publisher=CNET |date=2013-02-11 |accessdate=2013-12-20 |archive-date=2013-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220205824/http://news.cnet.com/8301-1023_3-57568826-93/microsofts-xbox-entertainment-studio-working-on-interactive-tv/ }}</ref>

2014年7月17日，微软证实该工作室将被关闭。<ref name="dawnchmielewski">{{cite web|url=http://recode.net/2014/07/17/microsoft-to-shut-down-xbox-entertainment-studios/|title=Microsoft to Shutter Xbox Entertainment Studios (Updated)|author=Dawn Chmielewski|work=Re/code|access-date=2015-11-20|archive-date=2016-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503023129/http://recode.net/2014/07/17/microsoft-to-shut-down-xbox-entertainment-studios/}}</ref>2014年10月29日，副总裁和公司总裁离开后，该公司正式关闭。<ref name="closure">{{citeweb|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/10/30/xbox-entertainment-studios-reportedly-shuttered-as-heads-leave|title=Xbox Entertainment Studios Reportedly Shuttered as Heads Leave|date=October 29, 2014|last=Pitcher|first=Jenna|accessdate=October 30, 2014|publisher=IGN}}</ref>

